text: Frederick VI or Friedrich VI may refer to: *Frederick VI, Duke of Swabia (1167–1191) *Frederick VI, Count of Zollern (died 1298) *Frederick VI, Margrave of Baden-Durlach (1617–1677) *Frederick VI, Landgrave of Hesse- Homburg (1769–1829) *Frederick VI of Denmark (1768–1839)
title: Frederick VI
